  const users = db.getUsers();
  res.json(users.map(({ id, name }) => ({ id, name }))); // email excluded
});
```

---

## 🔵 Low / Informational

### 7. Hardcoded Port & No Environment Separation (CWE-547)

**Problem:** Port `3000` is hardcoded. This makes it difficult to deploy consistently across environments and can lead to accidental exposure on unexpected ports.

```js
// ❌ Current
