const pinoHttp = require('pino-http');
const logger = pino();

app.use(pinoHttp({ logger }));
```

---

### 10. `timestamp` in `/health` May Aid Fingerprinting

Exposing the server's exact system time can assist timing-based attacks or help attackers fingerprint the infrastructure.

**Fix — remove or restrict to authenticated callers:**

```js
