### 8. 🟡 No HTTPS / Transport Security (OWASP A02)

**Issue:** The server listens on plain HTTP port 3000. All traffic — including auth tokens and user data — travels in cleartext.

**Fix:** In production, terminate TLS at a reverse proxy (nginx/load balancer) and force HTTPS. At the application level, enforce it with helmet's HSTS and an HTTP→HTTPS redirect:

```js
