### 4. No CORS Policy

**Issue:** Without an explicit CORS configuration, Express will respond to cross-origin requests using the browser's default permissive behavior. Depending on deployment, this could allow malicious sites to make credentialed requests to this API.

**OWASP:** A05 – Security Misconfiguration

**Fix:**
