| 5 | 🟠 Medium | A09 Logging & Monitoring | No logs or error handler | `morgan` + error middleware |
| 6 | 🟠 Medium | A04 Insecure Design | No rate limiting | `express-rate-limit` |
| 7 | 🟡 Low | A02 Sensitive Data | PII hardcoded in source | Externalize to DB/env |
| 8 | 🟡 Low | A05 Info Disclosure | Timestamp in health response | Remove timestamp |
| 9 | 🟡 Low | A04 Insecure Design | No body size limits | `express.json({ limit })` |

---

